<div class="story">
<p>Sanderling is an ocean to sound subdivision, consisting of over 250 lots, in the northern most end of Duck. Located just before you get to <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/corolla/pine-island.asp" title="Pine Island">Pine Island</a> in <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/corolla/" title="Corolla"> Corolla</a>, Sanderling is heavily vegetated and the original developers saved the vegetation so the streets are  lined with live oaks and myrtle bushes. Sanderling has an active home owners association which maintains the private roads and the ocean and sound access. The amenities include  a sound front pool and clubhouse, health club and tennis courts. You can find Sanderling just past <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/duck/gulls-flight.asp" title="Gulls'Flight">Gull's Flight</a>. </p>
